            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="230904618">
            飞机晚点但是起降没有明显的失重，差不多凌晨0:00到<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10030.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="三亚" target="_blank">三亚</a><a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10024.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="凤凰" target="_blank">凤凰</a>机场，<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10024.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="凤凰" target="_blank">凤凰</a>机场看上去挺小的，里面没有<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10513.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海口" target="_blank">海口</a>机场大，据说有免税店，不过和我这种XX应该没啥关系。<br />
首航晚班飞机给了一包花生米和一瓶怡宝矿泉水<img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v2/3@2x.png" style="width:28px;" /><br />
△选择首都航空有风险。。。其飞机取消几率大，而且改签只可以改首航和<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12938.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海南" target="_blank">海南</a>航空的航班。。。首都航空航班少o(╯□╰)o从<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10513.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海口" target="_blank">海口</a>回<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10132.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="厦门" target="_blank">厦门</a>航班取消就是教训
        </p>
            <div data-seq="230910892" data-index="4" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem">
                <h2 class="t7"><span class="_j_anchor">凤凰机场酒店</span></h2>
            </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="230910951">
            <a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10024.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="凤凰" target="_blank">凤凰</a>机场出来坐电梯上楼，出门往一号门方向走，走到4号门的位置就可以看到<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10024.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="凤凰" target="_blank">凤凰</a>机场酒店。酒店建在机场对面的商业城里，过个小马路坐电梯上来，和艺龙上显示的距离差不多，很近，不需要坐任何交通工具，不过酒店2017年初才营业，装修味有点重，价格一晚上330RMB（不包括早餐，早餐另外要88/人，不过晚餐也只有98元，早餐不划算晚餐在机场附近还是挺值得的）。附近还有个海航快捷酒店，这酒店建的比较早，加上和机场之间间隔着<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10024.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="凤凰" target="_blank">凤凰</a>机场动车站，其实需要联系酒店来接，但是一晚200RMB。这两酒店适合晚班机回市区不方便和赶早班机的。。<br />
<br />
<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10024.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="凤凰" target="_blank">凤凰</a>机场吃饭还算方便，不到100米就有麦当劳和星巴克，没有路边摊o(╯□╰)o但是早上要8点后才营业，星巴克要9点左右。<br />
交通也不错，穿过商业城下电梯就可以看到公交车站，公交车线路不多但是发车频次高。有到<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/196328.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="三亚湾" target="_blank">三亚湾</a><a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/16020.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="亚龙湾" target="_blank">亚龙湾</a><a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/196292.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海棠湾" target="_blank">海棠湾</a>的，去南山寺和大小洞天要转车，但是去天涯海角有直达公交车。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_230906568" data-seq="230906572" data-pid="230906568" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="105701">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_7344668/230906568.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/05/D0/wKgBZ1mCmLCAF16sAAcx3wmlwLY01.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/05/D0/wKgBZ1mCmLCAF16sAAcx3wmlwLY01.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="230906568" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/105701.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="105701" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="traffic"></i>三亚凤凰国际机场
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="230913090">
            进门是机器人带我们去，挺好玩的(*^__^*)&nbsp;
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_230906569" data-seq="230906573" data-pid="230906569" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="105701">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_7344668/230906569.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/05/EA/wKgBZ1mCmNKAWBhzAA0YSAA5tf481.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/05/EA/wKgBZ1mCmNKAWBhzAA0YSAA5tf481.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="230906569" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/105701.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="105701" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="traffic"></i>三亚凤凰国际机场
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_230906570" data-seq="230906574" data-pid="230906570" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="105701">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_7344668/230906570.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/05/F0/wKgBZ1mCmNqACz4dAAeZooaAq3M69.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/05/F0/wKgBZ1mCmNqACz4dAAeZooaAq3M69.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="230906570" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/105701.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="105701" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="traffic"></i>三亚凤凰国际机场
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_230906571" data-seq="230906575" data-pid="230906571" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="105701">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_7344668/230906571.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/05/F5/wKgBZ1mCmOGAfF2iAAprzysN3-c02.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" data-rt-src="https://c2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/05/F5/wKgBZ1mCmOGAfF2iAAprzysN3-c02.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="230906571" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/105701.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="105701" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="traffic"></i>三亚凤凰国际机场
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="230905838">
            第二天起个早，挺多赶早班机的人在那儿吃早餐。但是门口的麦当劳要8点才有吃的，选择余地少价格还贵o(╯□╰)o本来打算打包一份去南山寺和大小洞天吃的，后来发现除了煎饼没啥可带就forget&nbsp;it。
        </p>
            <div data-seq="230914163" data-index="5" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem">
                <h2 class="t6"><span class="_j_anchor">2</span></h2>
            </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="230914197">
            今天行程选择去南山寺和大小洞天，两个都是所谓5A景区。不过南山寺值，大小洞天进去后让我怀疑这怎么可能是5A<img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v2/16@2x.png" style="width:28px;" /><img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v2/16@2x.png" style="width:28px;" /><br />
<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12938.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海南" target="_blank">海南</a>岛的5A景区主要集中在<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10030.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="三亚" target="_blank">三亚</a>，南山寺、大小洞天、呀诺达热带森林、<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/14786.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="蜈支洲岛" target="_blank">蜈支洲岛</a>、分界洲岛，仅此五个，网上总是吹嘘自己是5A的事实上就是4A，包括著名的天涯海角也是4A。<br />
<br />
因为机场周围吃饭的8点后才有的吃，吃完麦当劳后就坐公交车8路到国光豪生，走到马路对面坐25路车（开往大小洞天，中间经过天涯海角西岛南山寺等景区）或者57路车（这路车没有到大小洞天，但是有到南山寺西岛天涯海角）。<br />
<br />
<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10030.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="三亚" target="_blank">三亚</a>公交车很贵很贵o(╯□╰)o从国光豪生酒店公交站到南山寺要10块钱，到大小洞天要12RMB<img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v2/14@2x.png" style="width:28px;" />
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_230918784" data-seq="230918827" data-pid="230918784" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="2280">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_7344668/230918784.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/0C/BD/wKgBZ1mCoPiADbpEAAeKJt3KAGA13.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/0C/BD/wKgBZ1mCoPiADbpEAAeKJt3KAGA13.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="230918784" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/2280.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="2280" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="hotel"></i>三亚国光豪生度假酒店
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="230919257">
            国光豪生沙滩就在国光豪生度假酒店对面，公交车下车后就是沙滩了，有躺椅可以坐，不需要money，有卖火龙果的，10块钱3个，还算便宜。当天因手上还拿着行李就木有买了。<br />
<br />
到对面坐公交车时，有出<a href="http://zuche.mafengwo.cn/jump_landing_page.php?keyword=%E7%A7%9F%E8%BD%A6" class="link" data-kw="租车"  target="_blank">租车</a>司机和一些地接的问要不要去南山寺天涯海角之类的，选择不理。<br />
<br />
在淘宝和蚂蜂窝上有看到去南山寺和大小洞天的团，差不多就是两地成人门票钱之和包接送，不过因为看上评价里对南山寺里的居士评价不高以及前一晚住的地点不是旅行团接车地点，就选择自由行了。<br />
<br />

        </p>
            <div data-seq="230921887" data-index="6" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem">
                <h2 class="t4"><span class="_j_anchor">长居南海愿——南山寺</span></h2>
            </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="230922850">
            从飞机上就可以看到<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/18142.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="南海" target="_blank">南海</a>观音了，那天晚上<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/18142.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="南海" target="_blank">南海</a>观音还亮着灯，很壮观。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_230918785" data-seq="230918828" data-pid="230918785" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="1234">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_7344668/230918785.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/0C/CC/wKgBZ1mCoQeAKdkXAAx-_JKq7j864.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/0C/CC/wKgBZ1mCoQeAKdkXAAx-_JKq7j864.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="230918785" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/1234.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="1234" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>南山文化旅游区
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="230920220">
            南山寺的小火车，30块一个人，固定站点上下，排队的人有点多，散客也挺多，提前一天在驴妈妈旅行网或者其它app上先订票会省10块钱，大小洞天会省20。学生票淡季61要当场买，买票的时候会被查，检票的时候人很多，工作人员一般也不管o(╯□╰)o别把学生证拿在手上让他一查就混进去。<br />
<br />
里面没必要去所谓的素斋自助吃饭，去那里吃饭的话就一定要坐小火车了，一进门就有很多吃的选择，一般一顿饭40起。水和饮料是外面的2~3倍。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_230918786" data-seq="230918829" data-pid="230918786" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="1234">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_7344668/230918786.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/0C/D6/wKgBZ1mCoRaAdaxrAAlA8nOp6pI71.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/0C/D6/wKgBZ1mCoRaAdaxrAAlA8nOp6pI71.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="230918786" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/1234.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="1234" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>南山文化旅游区
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="230921121">
            <a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/18142.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="南海" target="_blank">南海</a>观音背后的海真的很漂亮，拍照的时候不要正着照，朝圣的人很多。108米是从基座开始算起，<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/18142.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="南海" target="_blank">南海</a>观音实际上从底座上去是89米，很壮观。<br />
<br />
现在抱佛脚不需要另外付钱了。直接走过下面这座桥，跟随人群方向到佛的底座排队进去。有限制人数，夏天是淡季，差不多排队15~20分钟就进去了，如果到了旺季起码要1小时吧，不过里面真的很值得看。<br />
<br />
观音化身为33尊观音，顺时针参观，每尊观音形态各有特色，有工作人员带领我们参观第一个，剩下的都是自己参观的。抱佛脚可能要排队坐电梯或者走楼梯上去。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_230918787" data-seq="230918830" data-pid="230918787" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="1234">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_7344668/230918787.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/0C/DE/wKgBZ1mCoR6AEk_iAAYQaHIU4Lk83.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/0C/DE/wKgBZ1mCoR6AEk_iAAYQaHIU4Lk83.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="230918787" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/1234.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="1234" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>南山文化旅游区
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="230922516">
            到佛脚下顺时针抱佛脚，从那儿可以看到南山寺和南山塔。海水真的很清澈。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_230918788" data-seq="230918831" data-pid="230918788" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="1234">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_7344668/230918788.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/0C/F0/wKgBZ1mCoTKAapy_AApEjQikI9069.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/0C/F0/wKgBZ1mCoTKAapy_AApEjQikI9069.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="230918788" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/1234.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="1234" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>南山文化旅游区
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_230918789" data-seq="230918832" data-pid="230918789" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="1234">
