        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/1234.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="1234" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>南山文化旅游区
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_230918791" data-seq="230918834" data-pid="230918791" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="1234">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_7344668/230918791.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/0D/0B/wKgBZ1mCoVmACDSDABEHoNgl27w20.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/0D/0B/wKgBZ1mCoVmACDSDABEHoNgl27w20.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="230918791" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/1234.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="1234" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>南山文化旅游区
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <div data-seq="230921577" data-index="7" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem">
                <h2 class="t4"><span class="_j_anchor">碧海连天远，琼崖尽是春——大小洞天</span></h2>
            </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="230923303">
            南山寺只去<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/18142.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="南海" target="_blank">南海</a>观音抱佛脚差不多就要3小时了，再去<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10069.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="尼泊尔" target="_blank">尼泊尔</a>世博馆以及南山寺可能就木有时间去大小洞天了，抱着期待走到下车的停车场等公交车。<br />
<br />
25路公交车开往市区和大小洞天的是在同个地方下车，上车前记得问问有没有到大小洞天。等差不多15分钟，回市区的车比较多。
        </p>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="230923635">
            大小洞<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/62977.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="天门" target="_blank">天门</a>票108，驴妈妈买88，学生票需要查学信网信息o(╯□╰)o很严，当然可能是参观游客比较少，工作人员有时间查。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_230918792" data-seq="230918835" data-pid="230918792" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="17506">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_7344668/230918792.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/0D/13/wKgBZ1mCoWKAWCFYABKHSopjcFA79.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/0D/13/wKgBZ1mCoWKAWCFYABKHSopjcFA79.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="230918792" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/17506.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="17506" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>大小洞天
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="230924012">
            大小洞天属于道教圣地，崖州湾弧弦百里，碧波万倾；鳌山云深林翠，岩奇洞幽；海岸遍布神工鬼斧，肖形状物之大小磊群。有不少与老子相关。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_230918793" data-seq="230918836" data-pid="230918793" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="17506">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_7344668/230918793.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/0D/1A/wKgBZ1mCoWqAWUR9AA91HSjQr2094.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" data-rt-src="https://c2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/0D/1A/wKgBZ1mCoWqAWUR9AA91HSjQr2094.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="230918793" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/17506.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="17506" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>大小洞天
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_230918794" data-seq="230918837" data-pid="230918794" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="17506">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_7344668/230918794.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://a3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/0D/1F/wKgBZ1mCoXOAcJPRAAlzNfoccc025.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" data-rt-src="https://a3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/0D/1F/wKgBZ1mCoXOAcJPRAAlzNfoccc025.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="230918794" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/17506.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="17506" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>大小洞天
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_230918795" data-seq="230918838" data-pid="230918795" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="17506">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_7344668/230918795.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://a2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/0D/2A/wKgBZ1mCoX6AVg3uAAlLBTPT6Zk19.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" data-rt-src="https://a2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/0D/2A/wKgBZ1mCoX6AVg3uAAlLBTPT6Zk19.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="230918795" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/17506.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="17506" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>大小洞天
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="230924154">
            网上说大小洞天很多人拍结婚照，可能夏天天气炎热，没看见人拍结婚照。<br />
<br />
从南山回来脚有点酸，就花了15大洋坐了电瓶车，电瓶车有自动讲解，全程下来10多分钟，开的速度有点快，回来因为人比较少就招手停下，不过也有固定的几个站点，注意看沿路的路标。
        </p>
    
</div>
<div class="block-loading loading_forward"></div>

